Package group19.Entities

Class DoorKey

java.lang.Object
group19.Entities.Entity
group19.Entities.DoorKey
public class DoorKey extends Entity
Represents a Door key which consists of x,y coordinates. One can set its 'has been collected' state to True and get True/False whether it has been collected or not.
